data.description: A Charming, highly sought after Ranch Style Condo. In the highly desired Golf community. A Beautiful open floor plan. Neutrally painted, Highly maintained. 1st floor laundry. A Very spacious updated Kitchen, leading to a private deck and retractable awning for those sunny days.All appliances stay with the sale. Large Master suite, walk in closets. A Large Great room with Vaulted ceilings with a cozy fireplace. An open banister leading to a gorgeous professionally finished basement. It offers an additional full bath with tons of storage and closets.With an optional extra bedroom or office space. This Condo is a hard find. It wont last. Come take a peek. This is an Estate sale property, All data, sizes and information is approx and should be verified by  the BA.
data.whatILove: A Beautiful Ranch style Condo.A Charming floor plan that offers 2 bedrooms, 3 baths, A large Kitchen with all appliances. An open concept/spacious Great room with high ceilings.A spacious Mater suite bedroom.A Professionally finished basement and an attached two car garage.Centrally located in Canton with Plymouth/canton schools.A welcoming Condo Complex with many original owners.It offers many updates. Come take a peek, it is a must see!
